002package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.node;
003
004import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
005
006public interface INodeItemVisitable {
007  /**
008   * A visitor callback.
009   *
010   * @param <CONTEXT>
011   *          the type of the context parameter
012   * @param <RESULT>
013   *          the type of the visitor result
014   * @param visitor
015   *          the calling visitor
016   * @param context
017   *          a parameter used to pass contextual information between visitors
018   * @return the visitor result
019   */
020  <CONTEXT, RESULT> RESULT accept(@NonNull INodeItemVisitor<CONTEXT, RESULT> visitor, CONTEXT context);
021}
